<Class name="WsdlParameter" id="1fb7b1af-24e6-4431-9793-432de3b123b5">
    <superclass name="Object"/>
    <transient/>
    <persistentAllowed/>
    <sharedTransientAllowed/>
    <subclassPersistentAllowed/>
    <subclassSharedTransientAllowed/>
    <subclassTransientAllowed/>
    <transientAllowed/>
    <text>This class represents a parameter in a webservice method.

The parameter has a name (wsdlName) a type (wsdlTypeName)
and a usage (input, output, io etc).

wsdlTypeName may be the name of a class, in which case there
will exist a corresponding WsdlType instance, or it may be
a primitive wsdl type.

the possible values of 'usage' are:
Parameter.Usage_Constant
Parameter.Usage_Output
Parameter.Usage_IO etc</text>
    <DbClassMap file="richinternettoolset"/>
    <PrimAttribute name="usage" id="24bd99bc-8f7d-47bd-ad6e-2c3c93ca4638">
        <embedded/>
        <type name="Character"/>
    </PrimAttribute>
    <PrimAttribute name="wsdlName" id="e9eae893-5a8d-4248-adf0-7bc91dd48b2d">
        <type name="String"/>
    </PrimAttribute>
    <PrimAttribute name="wsdlTypeName" id="d97084f6-ebda-4401-bcdf-dfafa75483fd">
        <type name="String"/>
    </PrimAttribute>
</Class>
